{"tid":621422,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"丹尼路批紅魔：淨係識踢高波！","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T16:03:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2c641aa834ece3407d75a7d34cc081460ecf61","tid":621422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/870/20995464870/20999756277_600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F870%2F20995464870%2F20999756277_600x400.jpg&h=1a9e7a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Xtjo5GBSm4Pu%2BzG1FjlExIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=253b2f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼城後衛丹尼路雷斯在不敵曼聯後，批評對方進攻只懂長傳。<br />\n<br />\n在周六英超曼徹斯特打吡，曼城在半場領先2球之下，被曼聯反勝3:2，錄得今季主場首場敗仗之外，亦未能在今輪就確定封王。正選上陣的丹尼路雷斯（Danilo）賽後坦言十分失望。<br />\n<br />\n「我們踢得很好。要是你分析這場比賽，我們擁有控球權，控制了形勢，他們只是用長傳進攻，就入了3球。我們今季一直保持這種踢法，亦維持高水準，只是今天沒有效。」丹尼路說。<br />\n<br />\n藍月在周中歐聯8強次回合再於主場出擊，力爭扭轉首回合0:3的敗局，反勝利物浦晉級。丹尼路希望城迷能支持球隊：「他們今場很出色，事實上整季都很非常好，要是對紅軍時再接再厲，肯定會激勵我們爭取反勝。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"f242a77b88a562ffb325b18ca2954d20d4675471","tid":621422,"uid":174013,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jnzW8WDekno/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjnzW8WDekno%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=271c9f60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c7da0c487a07ffba18822e1e7c6c6fb953276c6","tid":621422,"uid":84081,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚兩球都燒味"},{"pid":"c886c648945961cb14f8965a5dea4e35812c30b7","tid":621422,"uid":111422,"like